"title": "7027: church, purpose and mission of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7027: church, purpose and mission of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The church is called to praise and glorify God, to establish Jesus Christ's kingdom, and to proclaim the gospel throughout the world.</p>\n<h2>God's purposes for the church</h2>\n<h3>To praise God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:5-Eph1:6\">EPH 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11-Eph1:12\">EPH 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:14\">EPH 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:15\">HEB 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>To share God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:29–8:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:43\">MAT 13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:23\">ROM 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26-Rev2:27\">REV 2:26–2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:4-Rev3:5\">REV 3:4–3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>God will build his church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18-Matt16:19\">MAT 16:18–16:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:40\">MAT 27:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:29\">MRK 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:19-John2:22\">JHN 2:19–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:9\">1CO 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:21–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:13\">EPH 4:11–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:3-Heb3:6\">HEB 3:3–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>To challenge Satan's dominion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:10-Eph3:11\">EPH 3:10–3:11</a></strong> <em>“rulers and authorities in the heavenly realms” refers to the powers of evil.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:14\">1JN 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>To go into the world in mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18\">2CO 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13-Matt5:16\">MAT 5:13–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:19–28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:48\">LUK 24:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21\">JHN 20:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15-Phil2:16\">PHP 2:15–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>The church's mission</h2>\n<h3>To preach the gospel to the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:10\">MRK 13:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:14\">MAT 24:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19\">MAT 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:47\">LUK 24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:47\">ACT 13:47</a></p>\n<h3>To do good to all</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:37-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:37–25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36\">ACT 9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Images of the church's mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13-Matt5:16\">MAT 5:13–5:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5-John15:8\">JHN 15:5–15:8</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:18-Matt7:19\">MAT 7:18–7:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4\">ROM 7:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:9-Eph5:10\">EPH 5:9–5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:11\">PHP 1:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:6\">COL 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:50\">MRK 9:50</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:34-Luke14:35\">LUK 14:34–14:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:12–13:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:5-1Thess5:6\">1TH 5:5–5:6</a></p>\n<h2>The growth of the church</h2>\n<h3>Numerical growth among the first Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:21\">ACT 11:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41\">ACT 2:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:47\">ACT 2:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:4\">ACT 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:14\">ACT 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">ACT 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:7\">ACT 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:42\">ACT 9:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:24\">ACT 11:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:24\">ACT 12:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:49\">ACT 13:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:5\">ACT 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:4\">ACT 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:8\">ACT 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:20\">ACT 19:20</a></p>\n<h3>The church is to grow to maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12-Eph4:13\">EPH 4:12–4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:15\">PHP 3:13–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Aspects of growth</h3>\n<p>Growth in character:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:10\">2CO 9:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:12\">1TH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a> <em>growth in understanding</em></p>\n<h3>Prayers for the growth of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:14-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:14–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:19\">EPH 1:17–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:11\">PHP 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9-Col1:12\">COL 1:9–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:11-1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:11–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11-2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:11–1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Visions of the church's final destiny</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:10\">REV 7:9–7:10</a></strong> <em>John's vision of the church in glory.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:31\">MAT 24:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:23\">HEB 12:22–12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>",
